// Windows executable icon resource.
// Resource ID 1 = the lowest numeric icon ID, which Windows Explorer / the
// shell use as the application icon for the .exe. The .ico is multi-size
// (16/24/32/48/64/128/256), all the maple-leaf badge — the OS picks the best
// size per context. Path is relative to this .rc file.
1 ICON "OpenChaos.ico"
